Doctor, thank you. I saw that the genetic sequence COVID-19 (provided for in COV-2) was 80-90% similar to SARS’ from 2003, and was wondering if that genetic similarity was abnormally high? Thanks again.
(Edit: purposely anonymous; genuine question)
